  <v-app id="home">
    <NavBar />
    <v-container fluid>

<script>
import { defineComponent } from 'vue';

// Components
import NavBar from '../components/NavBar.vue'

export default defineComponent({
  name: 'HomeView',

  components: {
    NavBar,
  },
});

<style>

.v-container{
  padding: 16px 0;
}

.header{
  position: relative;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
  height: 400px;
  width: 100%;
  color: white;
}
.header::before{
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  height: 100%;
  width: 50%;
  background: black;
  transform: skew(0deg, 5deg);
}

.header::after{
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 100%;
  width: 50%;
  background: black;
  transform: skew(0deg, -5deg);
}
</style>
